Participant ID
Please enter the Participant ID number you were given (e.g., P01, P02).
column3: Mental Demand: How much mental and perceptual activity was required (e.g., thinking, deciding, remembering, looking)?
column4: Physical Demand: How much physical activity was required (e.g., controlling your body, performing the exercises)?
column5: Temporal Demand (Time Pressure): How much time pressure did you feel due to the pace of the feedback or the exercise?
column6: Performance: How successful do you feel you were in performing the exercises correctly according to the system's guidance?
column7: Effort: How hard did you have to work (both mentally and physically) to accomplish your level of performance?
column8: Frustration Level: How insecure, discouraged, or irritated versus secure, gratified, and content did you feel during the task?
